WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.840
Welcome to Learn AI in 2

00:00:01.840 --> 00:00:02.640
minutes.

00:00:02.840 --> 00:00:05.360
Quick concept, simple metaphors and zeroes are

00:00:05.360 --> 00:00:06.160
gone over

00:00:05.880 --> 00:00:06.680
-road.

00:00:06.840 --> 00:00:09.300
You hear neural network everywhere in AI,

00:00:09.660 --> 00:00:11.180
but what actually is

00:00:11.180 --> 00:00:11.980
one?

00:00:12.380 --> 00:00:14.340
Think of neural network like an assembly

00:00:14.340 --> 00:00:15.140
line of decision

00:00:15.140 --> 00:00:15.940
makers.

00:00:16.300 --> 00:00:18.420
Data enters at one end, maybe a

00:00:18.420 --> 00:00:19.220
photo or a

00:00:19.180 --> 00:00:19.980
sentence.

00:00:20.180 --> 00:00:23.160
The first layer catches simple patterns, edges,

00:00:23.880 --> 00:00:25.840
basic shapes, or common world

00:00:25.840 --> 00:00:26.640
pairs.

00:00:26.920 --> 00:00:29.420
Each layer passes its finding to the

00:00:29.420 --> 00:00:31.740
next, which spots more complex

00:00:31.740 --> 00:00:32.540
patterns.

00:00:33.000 --> 00:00:35.720
By the final layer, the network combines

00:00:35.720 --> 00:00:38.300
all those signals into an

00:00:38.300 --> 00:00:39.100
answer.

00:00:39.460 --> 00:00:41.260
A cat or a dog, a spam

00:00:41.260 --> 00:00:42.600
or not spam, for

00:00:42.600 --> 00:00:43.400
example.

00:00:43.680 --> 00:00:46.260
It's inspired by the brain, but much,

00:00:46.260 --> 00:00:47.060
much

00:00:46.800 --> 00:00:47.600
simpler.

00:00:47.980 --> 00:00:50.240
It is just math layers stacked on

00:00:50.240 --> 00:00:51.040
each

00:00:50.540 --> 00:00:51.340
other.

00:00:51.360 --> 00:00:53.680
No single layer is smart alone, the

00:00:53.680 --> 00:00:55.360
power comes with the

00:00:55.360 --> 00:00:56.160
stack.

00:00:56.840 --> 00:00:59.080
Many simple steps building up to something

00:00:59.080 --> 00:00:59.880
useful.

00:01:00.620 --> 00:01:03.200
So remember, a neural network is stacked

00:01:03.200 --> 00:01:06.840
layers that detect patterns step by step,

00:01:07.240 --> 00:01:09.240
and simple pieces are smart

00:01:09.240 --> 00:01:10.040
together.

00:01:10.500 --> 00:01:11.400
That's your concept of the

00:01:11.400 --> 00:01:12.200
day.

00:01:12.100 --> 00:01:14.020
Follow for the next one, journey AI

00:01:14.020 --> 00:01:14.820
in 2

00:01:14.680 --> 00:01:15.480
minutes.

